  "content": "<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> The curse is drawn randomly at the start of class.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Players must find a way to lift the curse or suffer the effect for the entire session.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Some curses affect individual players, while others impact entire factions.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📖</font> Example Weekly Curses</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Curse Name</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Effect</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>How to Remove It</div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>The Mark of the Minotaur</div>",
